🏆 Sports Analytics Dashboard

A dynamic and interactive Sports Dashboard that provides real-time insights into matches, teams, and standings across multiple sports (including cricket, football, etc.). Built to visualize live, past, and upcoming match data in a clean and user-friendly interface.

---

🚀 Features

* View Live, Upcoming, and Past Matches
* Display Team Standings & Rankings
* Search and filter matches easily
* Real-time data using external APIs
* Interactive UI with smooth navigation
* Responsive design (mobile & desktop)

---

🛠️ Tech Stack

Frontend:

* React.js
* CSS / Tailwind

API:

* Sports Data API (live data integration)

---

⚙️ Installation & Setup

1. Install dependencies
   npm install

2. Run the project
   npm run dev

---

🔌 API Integration

* Fetches live data from sports APIs
* Handles:

  * Live matches
  * Team stats
  * League standings

---

🧠 Key Learnings

* Handling real-time API data
* Managing state in React
* Building scalable UI components
* Debugging API and UI issues

---

📌 Future Improvements

* Live score notifications
* Advanced analytics (graphs & charts)
* Multi-sport support expansion
* User authentication & favorites
* Performance optimization

